{"tid":620291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民族陣綫架「香港獨立」旗幟立會外集會支持戴耀廷","createTime":"2018-04-07T12:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T13:22:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"05d19a76cd2e50de79d7a88114c958ecb7ac78d6","tid":620291,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1389962_1_20180407201155.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1389962_1_20180407201155.jpg&h=a70c5b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣綫於立法會外舉行集會，支持港大法律系副教授戴耀廷，約有30人出席。民族陣綫成員架起「捍衛言論自由，打倒港版紅衞兵」橫額，以及「香港獨立」旗幟。<br />\n<br />\n有集會人士高叫「香港獨立」及「支持戴耀廷」口號，亦有樹仁大學學生會、恒生管理學院學生會及中文大學學生會的代表出席。有出席者表示，即使戴耀廷曾指不支持港獨，但認為要捍衛他談港獨的權利。<br />\n<br />\n民族陣綫表示，即使不認同戴耀廷部分理念，例如「雷動計劃」，但認為他正面對政治逼害，必須站出來聲援，又指本港現時的自由和法治都尤如鏡花水月，只要中央一紙命令就可以剝奪，所以香港必須脫離中國，才能政治自主。"},{"pid":"7d4947cfba941f6a0e1dd72d442bfc5a1fa6462e","tid":620291,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01bfd581f1c1b592f01ca9afa251adb6eca79967","tid":620291,"uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"7d4947cfba941f6a0e1dd72d442bfc5a1fa6462e","tid":620291,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:46:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛dewi<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/204603_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F204603_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7ec5eff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b7348f2e43c755bfffccff22c449b4a2bd0f15b7","tid":620291,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c290f6c856279983